## Introduction
The Gift Recommendation Chatbot is an AI-powered conversational agent designed to help users find the perfect gift based on their preferences, occasion, recipient details, and budget. The chatbot offers a personalized shopping experience, making it easier for users to select gifts for various events.

## Features
- **User Input Collection**: Gather relevant information such as occasion, recipient details, budget, and preferences.
- **Gift Recommendations**: Suggest a curated list of gifts based on user input.
- **Interactive Experience**: Engage users with follow-up questions for better recommendations.
- **Seamless Shopping Experience**: Guide users through the purchase process once a gift is selected.
- **Knowledge Base Integration**: Utilize a knowledge base for frequently asked questions and gift suggestions.

## Technologies Used
- [Dialogflow](https://dialogflow.cloud.google.com/) for natural language understanding and intent management.
- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) for backend support (if applicable).
- [Webhook services](https://cloud.google.com/functions) for dynamic gift recommendations.
- [GitHub](https://github.com/) for version control and collaboration.

